title: Cardi B vs. Nicki Minaj Back and Fourth
itunes:title: Cardi B vs. Nicki Minaj Back and Fourth
description:
Tuesday- Well Nicki Minaj and Cardi B was definitely the talk of the morning, but through all that back and forth they never encouraged people to vote. But speaking on voting, one person that is trying to get back the democratic vote is Hillary Clinton. However, with her comment, "They all look alike" about Cory Booker and Eric Holder who Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to. Moreover, we opened up the lines to see if our listeners thought Hillary Clinton may have went too far wit the comment or, if it was just jokes.
